- [ ] Idle connections are closed after configurable timeout (default 30s)
- [ ] Request processing has separate timeout (default 60s)
- [ ] Timeout uses asupersync Budget (not tokio::time)
- [ ] Graceful connection close (send Connection: close header)
- [ ] Tests verify timeout behavior
